                                                                                               NIST SP 800-161r1                               CYBERSECURITY SUPPLY CHAIN RISK MANAGEMENT
                                                                                                                                                  PRACTICES FOR SYSTEMS AND ORGANIZATIONS


                                                                                                Term                       Definition
                                                                                                                           Note 3: System-of-systems is included in the definition of
                                                                                                                           system.

                                                                                                system assurance           The justified confidence that the system functions as intended
                                                                                                [NDIA]                     and is free of exploitable vulnerabilities, either intentionally or
                                                                                                                           unintentionally designed or inserted as part of the system at
                                                                                                                           any time during the life cycle.
This publication is available free of charge from: https://doi.org/10.6028/NIST.SP.800-161r1




                                                                                                system component           A discrete identifiable information or operational technology
                                                                                                                           asset that represents a building block of a system and may
                                                                                                                           include hardware, software, and firmware.

                                                                                                system development life    The scope of activities associated with a system, encompassing
                                                                                                cycle                      the system’s initiation, development and acquisition,
                                                                                                [NIST SP 800-34 Rev. 1,    implementation, operation and maintenance, and ultimately its
                                                                                                adapted]                   disposal.
                                                                                                system integrator          Those organizations that provide customized services to the
                                                                                                                           acquirer including for example, custom development, test,
                                                                                                                           operations, and maintenance.
                                                                                                system owner (or program   Official responsible for the overall procurement, development,
                                                                                                manager)                   integration, modification, or operation and maintenance of a
                                                                                                [NIST SP 800-53 Rev. 5]    system.
                                                                                                threat                     Any circumstance or event with the potential to adversely
                                                                                                [NIST SP 800-53 Rev. 5]    impact organizational operations, organizational assets,
                                                                                                                           individuals, other organizations, or the Nation through a
                                                                                                                           system via unauthorized access, destruction, disclosure,
                                                                                                                           modification of information, and/or denial of service.

                                                                                                threat analysis            See threat assessment.

                                                                                                threat assessment          Formal description and evaluation of threat to a system or
                                                                                                [NIST SP 800-53 Rev. 5,    organization.
                                                                                                adapted]
                                                                                                threat event               An event or situation that has the potential for causing
                                                                                                [NIST SP 800-30 Rev. 1]    undesirable consequences or impact.
                                                                                                threat event outcome       The effect a threat acting upon a vulnerability has on the
                                                                                                                           confidentiality, integrity, and/or availability of the
                                                                                                                           organization’s operations, assets, or individuals.




